<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:15:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“时间不多了；美国驻以色列特使在人质协议推动中警告称，将没有生命可救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</link><description>卢大使反驳了内塔尼亚胡关于以色列国防军从加沙和费城走廊全面撤军是协议初始阶段的一部分的说法：“协议中没有提到费城走廊；起草框架时甚至没有考虑到这一点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡受到全球谴责，忙于躲避破坏人质交易的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</link><description>除了与外媒举行新闻发布会外，内塔尼亚胡还派了自己的心腹罗恩·德尔默前往美国媒体讨论人质谈判，因为总理担心美国媒体会更多地关注人质家属对他的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，大多数以色列人支持审查加沙战争社交媒体帖子，揭露犹太与阿拉伯之间的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</link><description>民意调查发现，政治分歧进一步影响了对审查制度的看法。在以色列右翼人士中，76% 的人希望封锁支持加沙平民的帖子，而左翼人士中只有 25% 的人愿意</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid i